{
  "stem": "12150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't march for days because as far-- I got shot in the last minute by an SS guard in the field right there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just for fun, he shot people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's no, no, no sense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't kill people, but he shot them anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wounded them, that's all, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One of my legs got shot one day before liberation by an SS guard who went crazy shooting people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I got shot, and I couldn't march anymore because of the-- I was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My foot was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was in a field and I was hiding behind a tree.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I figured whatever happens, happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So luckily, a day later, they came back with trucks-- SS and prisoners, helpers, strong prisoners and they picked up the people who were wounded.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apparently, those SS guards wanted to make a name for themselves before the Allies came in or to show or prove that they save people instead of hurting people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were taken to another camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as far as I remember, and we were placed in a clean barracks and not so many people in a barracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I figured there weren't so many of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All right, Harry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll stop you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one more tape and that's it?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
